data.text: Well, it seems the summer movie season is here! This week, John and El’Ahrai leap in feet-first with reviews of “The Fall Guy” and “Tarot”! Plus a newsbit segment that unexpectedly got away from us toward the end. (You’ll know it when you hear it.) Also, y’know, video picks, questions, the usual. You should listen! All these protocols and procedures to make it seem like you have it under control. But you’re a bunch of boys making models out of balsa wood! You don’t have anything under control!
